app_description:
Hi everyone, it's Jiji ASMR! Let's dive into today's Jelly Mukbang live!
Being a Mukbang streamer has always been Jiji's dream. Let's join the journey of little Jiji and watch as she takes her first steps into the world of ASMR streaming with her favorite treat - Jelly!
[What Jelly Should We Choose?]
Mix and match jelly flavors from sweet strawberry to tangy lemon, and even sprinkle in some surprising spicy jelly to keep your viewers amazed every Mukbang livestream!
[Mukbang Livestream]
Lights, camera, munch! Jiji's happiness shines as she enjoys her jelly with amazing ASMR sounds. Earn likes, shares, and donations by fulfilling viewer requests and engaging in quirky jelly challenges!
[Let's Go Shopping]
Sometimes you should try visiting the local supermarket. This place is truly a food lover's paradise with lot of of yummy food: Rainbow candy, mushroom noodles, matcha waffles, milk tea, pizza, malatang, pho and many more!
[Pick Your Vlogger Theme]
Decorate your ASMR livestream with cute pets, new food setups and beautiful backgrounds to keep your chat buzzing and your subscriber count soaring.
[Fun Minigames]
Join in minigames to make milk tea for your fans! You can also get money to buy more ingredients and foods.
Are you ready to help Jiji become the Queen of Mukbang? It's time to go live!
